    "title": "Example - NDWI temporal analysis",
    "description": "<h3>Background</h3><p>This example is created to present a concrete example of how the tools of the <a href=\"storm-platform.org/\">Storm ecosystem</a> can be used to create reproducible analysis.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>Application</h3><p>This example presents an NDWI time series analysis generated from a CBERS-4a/AWFI data cube. This data cube was developed and maintained by the <a href=\"http://brazildatacube.org/en/home-page-2/\">Brazil Data Cube project</a>, which was created and maintained by researchers at the National Institute for Space Research (INPE).</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
